  "title": "Proactive selective attention across competition contexts",
  "description": "This dataset investigates proactive selective attention mechanisms across different competitive contexts using neuroimaging data. The study examines how individuals modulate attentional resources in anticipation of task demands within varying levels of competition, providing insights into the neural correlates of goal-directed attention and performance optimization.",
